Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:59.94,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}想要时刻在你身边　时刻守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:04.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}除此之外别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:05.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:10.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}如果说　这都是你的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:15.78,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}若你想欺骗整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.70,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}ooh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:20.40,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那我也甘愿背叛一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:31.58,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我和你　在一起的时光虽不是永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:37.88,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}即使有一天我消失不见
